ll you when the next batch will be ready once this one goes.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">If the button below is still active, the current batch hasn't sold out yet.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUzNRL519Y_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggUzNRL519Y_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/h.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzSxlyVqRg_label","label":"ggzSxlyVqRg_label","default":"<p><span style=\"color:#17162E;font-size:px;\">Try Risk-Free</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWvY_WCyvN_text","label":"ggWvY_WCyvN_text","default":"<p>This is the part where you decide.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8Dp5QrHKP_text","label":"gg8Dp5QrHKP_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">You can close this page and nothing changes. Same mirror tomorrow morning. Same face. Same feeling.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Or you can do what my dad did. Twenty seconds. Before bed. And see what happens in 60 days.</span></p>"}],
